post_title: WTB: T206 Lou Fiene (Portrait) Carolina Brights and Drum
post_content: Probably a long shot, but it’s been awhile since I added any new cards to my Lou Fiene (Portrait) back run. I’m down to Carolina Brights and Drum to complete the back run. The graded pop on Drum is 0 and I doubt I could afford it, but would love to know if it exists.
